p: The study of the CEO, OEO and BEO composition has been previously reported by our group [ 35]. CEO content eugenol as main component (80.11%) and eugenol acetate (13.54%). D-limonene represents 97.93% of OEO composition and 49.38% of BEO composition. Other minor components are: β-myrcene (1.52%, in OEO), α-pinene (32.63%, in BEO), o-cymene (3.82%, in BEO), 4-carene (6.35%, in BEO), β-linalool (3.02%, in BEO) [ 35]. Other studies have reported D-limonene as the main component in OEO and BEO [ 36, 37, 38, 39] and eugenol in CEO [ 40].
